{"tid":942314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶與普通朋友既分別","createTime":"2018-12-15T15:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T17:44:47.000Z","uid":150979,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0683aaaf3480d1fd9a3b28c839dc8c502cf749bb","tid":942314,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">朋友</span></strong></span>:<br />\n無權知道對方既行蹤<br />\n無權決定對方既行為<br />\n有機會可以同對方<em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">扑野</span></em>  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">情侶</span></strong></span><br />\n無權知道對方既行蹤<br />\n無權決定對方既行為<br />\n有機會可以同對方<em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">扑野</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為自由，男女朋友都唔可以擁有特權！<br />\n因為自由，只想知道得更加深入，就被label 為恐怖情侶！<br />\n因為自由，男女朋友呢個身份顯得一文不值！<br />\n<br />\n繼績係愛情路上，用「<em>信任</em>」呢兩個字黎打飛機吧，哈哈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktqFMP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktqFMP7.jpg&h=fb1a9f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望你唔好成為下一個拓海。"},{"pid":"e73a086affc2524e5d9ec8593fbd97f30c38f4f1","tid":942314,"uid":83115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"點解朋友會有機會扑倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n情侶已經係比朋友高一級 唔覺得頭兩樣冇權喎"},{"pid":"9c0de95d71b8919632e616798a1b4ab800b1e093","tid":942314,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e73a086affc2524e5d9ec8593fbd97f30c38f4f1","tid":942314,"uid":83115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"點解朋友會有機會扑倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n情侶已經係比朋友高一級 唔覺得頭兩樣冇權喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"可能你圈子細，大把朋友之間扑野。<br />\n如果你覺得前兩樣係有權，well done!!!!!"},{"pid":"6565bd7ec8ac99499a6cbf42a89bdf951b5f520b","tid":942314,"uid":83115,"like":